OL,3,CHospital trust hit by maternity
OL,4,Cscandal lifted out of special measures
OL,6,FA hospital trust has been lifted out
OL,7,Fof special measures - seven years
OL,8,Fafter becoming embroiled in one of the
OL,9,Fcountry's worst maternity scandals.
OL,11,FShrewsbury and Telford Hospital NHS
OL,12,FTrust was put into special measures in
OL,13,FNovember 2018, after NHS England found
OL,14,Fissues with emergency and maternity
OL,15,Fcare, whistleblowing and governance.
OL,17,FBosses at the trust, which runs the
OL,18,FPrincess Royal Hospital in Telford and
OL,19,Fthe Royal Shrewsbury Hospital, said
OL,20,Fimprovement marks a "significant
OL,21,Fmilstone" and "pivotal moment".
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/3
