OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1772741478
OL,3,CHospital trust hit by maternity
OL,4,Cscandal lifted out of special measures
OL,6,FChief Executive Jo Williams said:
OL,7,F"This is not the end of our
OL,8,Fimprovement journey. We know that we
OL,9,Fhave much more still to do,
OL,10,Fparticularly in urgent and emergency
OL,11,Fcare, but we are making tangible
OL,12,Fprogress and we are pleased this has
OL,13,Fbeen recognised by NHS England and
OL,14,Fpartners.
OL,16,F"We will continue to listen, reflect
OL,17,Fand learn so we are always improving."
