PN,37303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1772741478
OL,3,CHospital trust hit by maternity
OL,4,Cscandal lifted out of special measures
OL,6,FA recent review by NHS England found
OL,7,Fthe trust had made strong progress in
OL,8,Fthe last 18 months, in finance,
OL,9,Fperformance and governance.
OL,11,FThe trust said it is now ranked 96 out
OL,12,Fof 134 in the national league tables,
OL,13,Fand second for diagnosing cancer
OL,14,Fwithin 28 days.
OL,16,FIt said there is more to do, including
OL,17,Fa multi-million pound investment
OL,18,Fthrough the Hospitals Transformation
OL,19,FProgramme by 2028.
